## Profitability Summary Table

| Tier | Revenue | Cost (Initial) | Margin (Initial) | Cost (Optimized) | Margin (Optimized) |
|------|---------|---------------|------------------|------------------|-------------------|
| Starter | $500 | $875 | -75% | $525 | -5% |
